      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Elf Elder$<BR>You've come.<BR>I would prefer the problems of the Forest of New Moon to be solved by the Elves…<BR>But things always go the way we want them to be.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
